title: Commercial Office, Studio, Workshop space - Rent your space today
description: Print Village offers innovative work spaces for small and start-up businesses of all types from art studios to blacksmiths.
• Electric, Water, Business Rates and fast fibre included
• Help with couriers, packages, logistics if you are away
• Daily cleaning service for the communal areas
• Complimentary use of forklift on site
• Complimentary car parking during normal office hours and secure storage for your bike

• What`s more Print Village`s units are easy to get to-they are just a few minutes away from Peckham Rye railway station from where you can get to London Victoria or Clapham Junction in just 15 minutes! Outside there is a vibrant environment of restaurants and excellent coffee shops.
We offer you a community, not just a workplace!
Please get in touch with our sales team in business hours to arrange a viewing!
